subject: Basketball (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kaleena Mosqueda-Lewis scored 15 of her 17 points in the first half and fourth-ranked UConn beat No. 23 Rutgers, 49-34, on Sunday night in the quarterfinals of the Big East tournament in Hartford.
